    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless, smoke-free, and garage-kept. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it. It's a total dream to drive and I'd love for you to come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 43900.0,
