    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a definitive 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, it is flawless; the high-pressure VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has received proactive structural reinforcement\u2014a critical upgrade for the discerning collector. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec bushings and an uncompromised suspension geometry. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with no evidence of road rash. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters are firm and free of typical wear, while the instrument cluster remains free of pixel degradation. This is a turnkey, investment-quality icon with a clean DME report.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
