      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine, mint condition\u2014it seriously looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, so it's practically flawless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! I'd love for you to come see it for yourself\u2014let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
